    <shortdesc class="- topic/shortdesc " xtrc="shortdesc:1;5:17" xtrf="file:/C:/Users/phlinss/Documents/Dita_Handburch%20CAGB/Update_Arbeitsumgebung"/><prolog class="- topic/prolog "><author class="- topic/author " xtrc="author:1;12:17" xtrf="file:/C:/Users/phlinss/Documents/Dita_Handburch%20CAGB/bookmap.ditamap">Berlin-Brandenburgische Akademie der Wissenschaften TELOTA -Arbeitsgruppe
